program.statement:
Unconditional atom-scale residual flatness remains open. After trade-weight law, the residual multi-mate wall splits as:
  min-weight tight cliques → K_res ≤ 18 if pairwise-tight;
  long trades → class (ii) partial plant or (iii) coset-free;
  free≤1 → already packed (wrong free for deployed).
To close unconditionally need: residual forbids long trades AND residual min-weight fibers are pairwise-tight cliques of size ≤ 18 (or ≤ 1), OR bound U_phi / U_res directly.
